    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level when you choose this presence, you apply your wit to control the field of battle as well as social interactions. You can use your Intelligence modifier in place of your Charisma modifier for all your warlord features, and you gain proficiency in one of the following skills of your choice: Arcana, History, Investigation, Nature, Religion or a language of your choice.</p><p>Furthermore, you can use your Intelligence modifier instead of your Wisdom modifier or Charisma modifier when making Wisdom or Charisma checks. You may do this a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest.</p>",
